commitResults.messageBody:
Previously 'find y/1' will only return entries with experience == 1.
This functionality might not be conveneint for recruiters to use because it is unnecessarily restrictive.
If the user types 'find y/1' now, all entries with years of experience more than 1 year will be returned.
